---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Grazie — ITMatch"
  description="Abbiamo ricevuto la tua richiesta di demo ITMatch."
>
  <Header lang="it" />

  <section class="grazie">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="check-ic">✓</div>
      <h1>Richiesta ricevuta.</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        Grazie! Abbiamo ricevuto la tua richiesta di demo.
        Ti ricontattiamo a breve per mostrarti il matching AI su una posizione reale.
      </p>
      <div class="cta-row">
        <a href="https://www.itmatch.app/" class="btn btn-accent">Torna alla home</a>
        <a href="https://www.itmatch.app/#screening" class="btn-ghost">Scopri l'AI Screening</a>
      </div>
      <p class="exp">Nel frattempo, dai un'occhiata a come ITMatch automatizza ricerca, matching e screening dei candidati IT.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer lang="it" />
</Layout>

<style>
  .grazie {
    padding: 120px 0 130px;
    text-align: center;
    background: radial-gradient(120% 70% at 50% 0%, var(--brand-50) 0%, #fff 60%);
    min-height: 60vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .check-ic {
    width: 72px; height: 72px;
    margin: 0 auto 28px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--match);
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 38px;
    font-weight: 700;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    box-shadow: 0 14px 34px -10px rgba(16,185,129,.5);
  }
  .grazie h1 { font-size: 52px; line-height: 1.05; color: var(--ink); margin: 0 0 20px; }
  .lead { font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.6; color: var(--muted); max-width: 52ch; margin: 0 auto 34px; }
  .cta-row { display: flex; gap: 22px; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
  .exp { font-size: 14px; color: var(--muted-2); margin: 40px auto 0; max-width: 50ch; line-height: 1.6; }
  @media (max-width: 720px) {
    .grazie { padding: 80px 0 90px; }
    .grazie h1 { font-size: 36px; }
    .lead { font-size: 17px; }
    .cta-row { flex-direction: column; gap: 16px; }
  }
</style>
